Properties.Caption: Просмотр источников финансирования
Properties.Tag: Select [K_D].[CD] As [Источник фин], Max([K_D].[NS]) As [Наименование источника фин], [K_BK].[CBK] As [Код БК], Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 1) Mod 2) As [Знак плюс], Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 2) Mod 2) As [Знак минус], Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 4) Mod 2) As [Продажа имущества], Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 16) Mod 2) As [Коммерческая деятельность 1], Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 32) Mod 2) As [Остатки средств], Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 64) Mod 2) As [Внешний], Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 1048576) Mod 2) As [Используется МО с д], Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 8388608) Mod 2) As [Закрыто] From ((([K_D] With (NoLock) Inner Join [K_BK] With (NoLock) On ([K_D].[K_BKID]=[K_BK].[K_BKID])) Left Join [K_D] As [K_D_1] With (NoLock) On ([K_D].[K_DID_PARENT]=[K_D_1].[K_DID])) Left Join [K_D] As [K_D_2] With (NoLock) On ([K_D].[K_DID_PARENT_PLAN]=[K_D_2].[K_DID])) Where [K_D].[K_D_TYPE]=2 And |0 Group by [K_D].[CD], [K_BK].[CBK], Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 1) Mod 2), Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 2) Mod 2), Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 4) Mod 2), Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 16) Mod 2), Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 32) Mod 2), Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 64) Mod 2), Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 1048576) Mod 2), Sgn(Int([K_D].[FLAGS] / 8388608) Mod 2) Order by |1
